The mail/ subdir contains a sample result of running 'cft -w mail';
initially found in /tmp/cft/mail

mail/changes - log of raw changes received from gamin
mail/std{err,out} - streams from cft deamon for debugging
mail/orig/ - preserved original files (from invoking 'cft -o mail'
mail/after/ - changed files at the time 'cft -k mail' was run